---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Hotel Iubit" description="Learn more about Terms & Conditions at Hotel Iubit.">
  <div class="bg-primary text-white py-20 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="py-20 bg-background min-h-[50vh]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl prose prose-lg">
      <p>Last updated: July 23, 2026</p>
      
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>Welcome to Hotel Iubit. These Terms and Conditions govern your use of our website and your stay at our hotel. By making a reservation or using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms.</p>
      
      <h2>2. Booking and Reservations</h2>
      <p>We offer room accommodations that can be booked online through our website, in person at our front desk, or over the phone. All bookings are subject to availability and confirmation.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You must be at least 18 years old to make a reservation.</li>
        <li>A valid credit card or advance deposit may be required to secure your booking.</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to cancel or modify reservations where it appears that a customer has engaged in fraudulent or inappropriate activity.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>3. Room Rates and Extra Charges</h2>
      <p>Our standard rates cover the cost of your room accommodation only. Additional services are not included in the base room rate unless explicitly stated.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Meals and Dining:</strong> All meals, including breakfast, lunch, and dinner, incur extra charges and are not included in the standard room rate.</li>
        <li><strong>Other Services:</strong> Any additional amenities or services requested during your stay may result in supplementary fees.</li>
        <li>All prices are subject to applicable local taxes and fees.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>4. Check-in and Check-out</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Check-in:</strong> A valid government-issued ID and a payment method for incidentals are required upon arrival.</li>
        <li><strong>Check-out:</strong> Guests must check out by our designated check-out time. Late check-outs may result in additional charges.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>5. Cancellations and Refunds</h2>
      <p>Our cancellation policy varies depending on the rate type you have selected. Please review the specific cancellation terms provided at the time of your booking. Failure to arrive for your reservation without prior notice may result in a "no-show" charge.</p>
      
      <h2>6. Guest Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>Guests are expected to conduct themselves respectfully and avoid disrupting other guests. Any damage to hotel property caused by you or your party will be charged to your account.</p>
      
      <h2>7. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms and Conditions, please reach out to our front desk, call us, or send us an email.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
